{
  "stem": "10905.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going and when we arrive, money or trucks, or whatever was going to go into the hands of the-- of the Gestapo, and the SS, and the-- and the German army.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, knew for sure?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew that they were killing Jews left and right, but the-- the scope of the extermination of Jews was not known.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- definitely not by my parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can guarantee 100% they didn't even know about the gassings, and I'll tell you later on why.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, [INTERPOSING VOICES] Goethe once said, Man sieht was man weiss.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you know something, you see it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If-- if you-- if it is-- if it is humanly non-believable, even if you see it, you're not gonna believe it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So nobody wants to die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody wants to believe the worst possible thing from another human being.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think anybody knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Our group was a very interesting makeup of group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was Zionists, Hungarian Zionists.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was some family of the gentlemen who were negotiating, Kasztner and Brand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the Satmar Rabbi Yoel Teitelbaum who hated the Zionists, not hated, he disliked the Zionists.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't believe in Zion because until the Messiah were to come, there's not gonna be a Zion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He and his entourage were saved by the Hungarian Zionists in this group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know perhaps, 50 or 100 Polish orphan children who somehow managed to get to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I said, the train came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the train arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there was some negotiating problems with the Austrians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were on the Austrian Hungarian border for several days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The train was just stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very hot summertime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were you allowed to get out of the train?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
